<p>
Emacs is a malleable system, so everybody will have their personal preferences to undertake a task. Any article on how to use Emacs is thus opinionated. If you have a different way of doing things, please complete the <a href="https://lucidmanager.org/contact/">contact form</a> to send me an email or contact me on social media.</p>
